      "Generation method: Nuclear",
      "Transmission voltage: 132 kV"
    ],
    "hint": "Identify the energy source mentioned in the text for the generation method. For the voltage, recall that UK transmission voltages are strictly 132 kV, 275 kV, or 400 kV."
  }
}

